<div class="container mb-5 pb-5">
<h2 class="page_title mb-3 mt-3 has text-center">Drop your message below:</h2>
<h4 class="page_title has text-center mb-3 ml-5">Do you have any suggestion or feedback?<br> We would love to hear from you!</h4>


 <div class="row pb-2">
 	<div class="ml-5 mt-5">
 	- Call us on:<a class="has text-warning"> 0788561729</a><br>
 	- Whatsapp:<a class="has text-warning"> 0788561729</a></div>
    <h2 class="text-center ml-5 pl-5">Contact Us:</h2>
    <div class="col-md-5"> 

    <div class="card mt-2"><p class="page_title has text-white has text-center">Please, fill in the form below and we will get back to you as soon as we get your message.</p><div class="bg-warning">

